Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The most crucial moment in life is during decision making.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But also instilled \Nnumerous lessons on how to live.{unsure, lit is "for the sake of living, precepts, numerous left behind"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:31.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,700)\c&H0007DF&\fs100\b1\bord0\blur1}Animentary\N{\b\c&HE0DBF3&}Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,30,,Wit is your weapon{honestly no clue what is megurase here, deepl says "rack one's brain"}\NRemember to use your head{智恵をめぐらせ 頭を使え}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,30,,Repress your anguish, \NIf you are a man{悩み抜け抜け 男なら}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,30,,One decision is enough \NTo make others cry or laugh{泣くも笑うも 決断ひとつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,30,,If you win, don't hold your head high, \NIf you lose, don't cry{勝っておごるな 敗れて泣くな}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:14.57,Default,,0,0,30,,Men, don't you ever let others see your tears{男 涙は見せぬもの}
Comment: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ch}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:24:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)}The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace.\NBut also instilled numerous lessons on how to live.{太平洋戦争はわれわれに平和の尊さを教えたがまた生きるための教訓を数多くのこしている}
Comment: 0,0:24:43.11,0:24:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{ch}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:47.56,Default,,0,0,50,,If you're a man, let's put your strength to test{男だったら　力を試せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:51.90,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, keep your hopes sizzling{男だったら　希望(のぞみ)を燃やせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.90,0:24:56.26,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, don't lose your heart{男だったら　くじけるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:25:04.83,Default,,0,0,50,,Because there's just you and me, a man and a man{俺もおまえも　男と男}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:13.06,Default,,0,0,50,,With crimson blood flowing in our veins all the same{おなじ真赤な　血が通う}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:12.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,700)}Brought to you by the Sorcery Party \Nѫ~ѫ\N"Lux in Tenebris"
